Morning Star flew through the air away from the Predacon base.  until he
saw a group of Maximals preparing for battle.  He landed on top of a
hilltop and decided to have a little fun.  He transformed into Robot mode
and started to twirl is hand in a circle.  As he did so, the clouds above
the Maximals started to converge and spiral.  With his other hand, he
started to make a circle go in the other direction.  Rain started to
fall, and then Lightning striking at the battle ready Maximals.
